dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her school friend\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"twoimpressive performanceson\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"the European circuit\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was no way that wedding was going to go ahead and I was not going to be there.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no way\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"wedding\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After I came back from Paris we spent the whole day wedding dress shopping.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1589, \"end\": 1594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0225638393837526e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the whole day\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a really good way to bring an end to a season that's been a lot of change for me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really good way\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"an end\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"a season\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1712}, {\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asher-Smith made the bold move to the US last winter, amicably splitting from her long-time coach John Blackie.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1771, \"end\": 1773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9859943084159629, \"rank\": 0.011110874038592193, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1836, \"end\": 1843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blackie_and_Son\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.297181947650312e-14, \"text\": \"Blackie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blackie_and_Son\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blackie_and_Son\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Asher-Smith\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"the bold move\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"her long-time coach\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She joined the stable of highly regarded US trainer Edrick 'Flo' Floreal to work alongside a raft of leading sprinters, includingthe new Olympic 100m champion Julien Alfred.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1886, \"end\": 1888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9859943084159629, \"rank\": 0.011110874038592193, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stable\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"a raft\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"leading sprinters\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision has been vindicated.\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decision\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although her tearful100m semi-final eliminationmay have been a lasting image of her Olympics, it was hardly a fair depiction of her season.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her tearful100m semi-final eliminationmay\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"a lasting image\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympics\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"a fair depiction\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2178}, {\"ngram\": \"her season\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She bounced back to finish an agonising fourth in the 200m final and win silver in the 4x100m, in a summer which began with 100m gold at the European Championships and ended with fast times in the Diamond League.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2391, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.425216949716361e-18, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an agonising fourth\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2240}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4x100m\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2287}, {\"ngram\": \"a summer\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"100m gold\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2327}, {\"ngram\": \"the European Championships\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"fast times\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After spending the year immersing herself in fresh ideas, surrounded by impossibly high standards, Asher-Smith has breathed new life into her career, staying fit and running as fast as ever.\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2431}, {\"ngram\": \"fresh ideas\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"impossibly high standards\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"Asher-Smith\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2518}, {\"ngram\": \"new life\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really excited by running in track and field right now, which I think I do owe to a shake-up in environment,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2640}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"a shake-up\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"environment\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was absolutely nothing wrong with where I was in London - I absolutely love my previous coach, John, he's like a second dad.\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2782, \"end\": 2788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 2.456109105158373e-11, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"absolutely nothing\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"my previous coach\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2826}, {\"ngram\": \"John\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2832}, {\"ngram\": \"a second dad\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just sometimes change is mentally good and stimulating.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's brought a new perspective and it's made everything really exciting again.\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new perspective\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's having new reference points, and people with a new eye looking at you and going, 'Oh, you can do that, crazy', and I have just taken it for granted and been like, that's normal for me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3190, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new reference points\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3044}, {\"ngram\": \"a new eye\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I made a mistake, and then I corrected it, and went and did really well in the last three Diamond Leagues It is the first time in her life Asher-Smith has lived anywhere else for a sustained period and she is, she admits, a fish out of water in Austin.\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3438, \"end\": 3444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Cold_Steve_Austin\", \"score\": 0.8585635363225783, \"rank\": 0.16464962576408945, \"text\": \"Austin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Cold_Steve_Austin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Cold_Steve_Austin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3208}, {\"ngram\": \"the last three Diamond Leagues\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3297}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3318}, {\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3330}, {\"ngram\": \"Asher-Smith\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3342}, {\"ngram\": \"a sustained period\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3389}, {\"ngram\": \"a fish\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3420}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's really, really hot.\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wake up every day and the first thing in my head is to make sure I am hydrating.\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first thing\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3512}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know if I have not set up my day drinking water, drinking my electrolytes from the moment I am up, training is not going to go well\\u2026 \\\"Just being able to experience a different way of life is really stimulating.\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my day\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3590}, {\"ngram\": \"drinking water\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3605}, {\"ngram\": \"my electrolytes\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3631}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3647}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3665}, {\"ngram\": \"a different way\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3737}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They love their barbecues, love their tacos.\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their barbecues\", \"from\": 3780, \"to\": 3795}, {\"ngram\": \"their tacos\", \"from\": 3802, \"to\": 3813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The biggest change is the thing that they do for relaxing, which is chilling by the pool with their friends,\\\" she laughs, \\\"which is nice for me as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 3968, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The biggest change\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 3833}, {\"ngram\": \"the thing\", \"from\": 3837, \"to\": 3846}, {\"ngram\": \"relaxing\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3872}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3903}, {\"ngram\": \"their friends\", \"from\": 3909, \"to\": 3922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has taken an interest in the upcoming US election, while managing to avoid any sticky conversations.\", \"from\": 3970, \"to\": 4074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4012, \"end\": 4014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9859943084159629, \"rank\": 0.011110874038592193, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interest\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 3995}, {\"ngram\": \"any sticky conversations\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Austin is a liberal city anyway,\\\" she smiles.\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4076, \"end\": 4082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Cold_Steve_Austin\", \"